ABOUT//

getxkcd v1.0!

getxkcd is a tool for downloading and updating a collection of comics from popular webcomic xkcd.com. Simply put it in an empty directory and run it to fill that directory with every comic. Then whenever you want to update your collection, simply run it again. It is a fork of Fetch-XKCD by WinButler.

getxkcd was written in Python 2.7.3 and may not work in Python 3.x.

USAGE//

Place getxkcd.py into an empty directory and run it. To bring your collection up to date, run it again.

optional arguments:
  -h, --help              show this help message and exit